You should be using a test case - look up testing on truffle docs for this 
Inside an "it" case you should then specify the deployed contract:
var myContract = Payable.deployed();
You can then transfer a payment to the contract like so: 
myContract.call({value: web3.toWei(0.5, "ether"), from: accounts[1]}); 
